Executive Summary
ICD ResearchsAVG Technologies N.V. - Company Profile and Financial Analysis contains in depth information and data about the company and its operations. The profile contains a company overview, key facts, major products and services, financial ratios, financial analysis, recent developments, key employees, company locations and subsidiaries.
Key Findings
This report is a crucial resource for industry executives and anyone looking to access key information about AVG Technologies N.V.
The report utilizes a wide range of primary and secondary sources, which are analyzed and presented in a consistent and easily accessible format. ICD Research strictly follows a standardized research methodology to ensure high levels of data quality and these characteristics guarantee a unique report.
Synopsis
Identifies crucial company information about AVG Technologies N.V. along with major products and services for business intelligence requirements.
Provides key ratios on companysfinancial performance.
Identifies key employees to assist with key business decisions.
Provides annual and interim financial ratios.
Reasons To Buy
Enhance your understanding of AVG Technologies N.V.
Increase business/sales activities by understanding customers businesses better.
Recognize potential partnerships and suppliers.
Qualify prospective partners, affiliates or suppliers.
Acquire up-to-date company information and an understanding of the companysfinancial health.
Key Highlights
AVG Technologies N.V. (AVG) is an information technology service provider. The company provides software solutions and online services such as PC and mobile security, cloud based desktop management, location services, optimization and online privacy. It provides security services for devices, data and people. AVG provides products and services to provide internet security, performance optimization, personal privacy and identity protection. The company markets its products under the brands AVG, The Online Security Company, Devices. Data. People, AVG PrivacyFix, AVG CloudCare and AVG LiveKive. AVG provides services for personal computers, MAC, Mobiles and Tablets. It also offers business solutions such as AVG Internet Security Business Edition, AVG File Server Edition, AVG Antivirus Business Edition and AVG PC TuneUp Business Edition. The company partners with managed service provider, value added reseller and IT solutions provider, to provide its products and services. It markets and distributes its products and services through its resellers worldwide. AVG is headquartered in Amsterdam, The Netherlands.
