^ a b "Original RickRoll Video Returns to YouTube After 24-Hour Copyright Hiatus". MaximumPC. 24 May 2012. Retrieved 26 May 2012. 
^ a b "News of 'Rickroll' meme death greatly exaggerated". MSNBC. 25 May 2012. Archived from the original on 26 May 2012. Retrieved 26 May 2012. 
^ "RickRoll'D - YouTube". YouTube. 15 May 2007. Retrieved 26 May 2012. 
^ a b Protalinski, Emil. "AVG Security Toolbar is the worst foistware I've ever seen | ZDNet". ZDNet. Retrieved 2016-09-22. 
^ "How do I make these AVG popups STOP??? | AVG". 2015-08-13. Retrieved 2016-09-22. 
^ "Don’t Use Your Antivirus’ Browser Extensions: They Can Actually Make You Less Safe". Retrieved 2016-09-22. 


